  <entry>
    <title>Database practice</title>
    <url>/2024/05/07/Database%20practice/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>这是我们数据库课程的数据库使用练习，如果你对更多数据库知识感兴趣，可以通过页面底部的GitHub联系我。Happy Coding!</p>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="1-创建用户"><a href="#1-创建用户" class="headerlink" title="1.创建用户"></a>1.创建用户</h1><h4 id="大数据库的用户，在ALTER切换数据库之前"><a href="#大数据库的用户，在ALTER切换数据库之前" class="headerlink" title="大数据库的用户，在ALTER切换数据库之前"></a>大数据库的用户，在ALTER切换数据库之前</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">create</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">user</span> c##wshust identified <span class="hljs-keyword">by</span> wtsgyh1972; #必须要加‘c##’<br><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>  <span class="hljs-keyword">GRANT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">connect</span>,resource <span class="hljs-keyword">to</span> c##wshust; #DRUGDB是大数据库，创建用户和授权都要在大数据库下操作<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>在图形化界面中连接</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs clean">用户名：c##wshust<br>密码：wtsgyh1972<br>角色：默认<br>主机名：<span class="hljs-number">210.42</span><span class="hljs-number">.105</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span> （改成你自己的主机ip）<br>端口：<span class="hljs-number">1521</span><br>SID：DRUGDB<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>在终端连接</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ sqlplus c<span class="hljs-comment">##wshust/wtsgyh1972@DRUGDB</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> conn c##wshust<span class="hljs-operator">/</span>wtsgyh1972<span class="hljs-variable">@DRUGDB</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<h4 id="单数据库用户"><a href="#单数据库用户" class="headerlink" title="单数据库用户"></a>单数据库用户</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">alter</span> session <span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> container<span class="hljs-operator">=</span>PDBDRUGDB;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">user</span> wshust identified <span class="hljs-keyword">by</span> wtsgyh1972;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">GRANT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">CONNECT</span>,RESOURCE <span class="hljs-keyword">TO</span> wshust; #PDBDRUGDB是小数据库，创建用户和授权都要在这个数据库下操作<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>在图形化界面中连接</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight armasm"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs armasm">用户名：wshust<br>密码：wtsgyh1972<br>角色：默认<br>主机名：<span class="hljs-number">210</span>.<span class="hljs-number">42</span>.<span class="hljs-number">105</span>.<span class="hljs-number">1</span> （改成你自己的主机<span class="hljs-built_in">ip</span>）<br>端口：<span class="hljs-number">1521</span><br>服务名：PDBDRUGDB<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>在终端连接</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ sqlplus wshust/wtsgyh1972@PDBDRUGDB<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> conn wshust<span class="hljs-operator">/</span>wtsgyh1972<span class="hljs-variable">@PDBDRUGDB</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h1 id="2-切换用户"><a href="#2-切换用户" class="headerlink" title="2.切换用户"></a>2.切换用户</h1><p><strong>从bash以sys用户进入sql命令行</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ sqlplus sys/wtsgyh1972@DRUGDB as sysdba<br>$ sqlplus / as sysdba<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>从bash以HR用户进入sql命令行</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ sqlplus HR/HR@PDBDRUGDB<br>$ sqlplus HR/HR@210.42.105.1:1521/PDBDRUGDB <span class="hljs-comment">#这种命令允许指定ip</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>从sql切换sys用户</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> conn sys<span class="hljs-operator">/</span>wtsgyh1972<span class="hljs-variable">@DRUGDB</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> sysdba<br><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> conn <span class="hljs-operator">/</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> sysdba<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>从sql切换HR用户</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> conn HR<span class="hljs-operator">/</span>HR<span class="hljs-variable">@PDBDRUGDB</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> conn HR<span class="hljs-operator">/</span>HR<span class="hljs-variable">@210</span><span class="hljs-number">.42</span><span class="hljs-number">.105</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">1521</span><span class="hljs-operator">/</span>PDBDRUGDB<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h1 id="3-更改用户密码"><a href="#3-更改用户密码" class="headerlink" title="3.更改用户密码"></a>3.更改用户密码</h1><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql"><span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">password</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> 用户名@localhost = <span class="hljs-keyword">password</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;新密码&#x27;</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">set</span> password <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> HR<span class="hljs-variable">@210</span><span class="hljs-number">.42</span><span class="hljs-number">.105</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> password(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;123&#x27;</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh">ALTER <span class="hljs-keyword">USER</span> <span class="hljs-title">用户名@localhost</span> IDENTIFIED BY 新密码;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SQL</span><span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">ALTER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">USER</span> HR<span class="hljs-variable">@210</span><span class="hljs-number">.42</span><span class="hljs-number">.105</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span> IDENTIFIED <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> <span class="hljs-number">123</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>数据库</category>
      </categories>
